WEBVTT

01:36.800 --> 01:37.680
Madam.

01:38.000 --> 01:39.280
I won't go in.

01:39.759 --> 01:40.640
I,

01:41.479 --> 01:42.960
I'll just wait in the yard.

03:03.600 --> 03:05.040
Bastards, idiots,

03:05.120 --> 03:06.180
a bunch of cowards.

03:06.320 --> 03:07.120
Stop yelling.

03:07.720 --> 03:08.960
Uncle is in the room.

03:11.720 --> 03:13.650
Tell him I won't be back for a while.

03:14.080 --> 03:15.400
Fengnian.

03:20.880 --> 03:21.840
Uncle.

03:24.200 --> 03:25.120
Uncle is here.

03:27.680 --> 03:29.600
How is your health?

03:30.560 --> 03:31.400
Pour some tea.

03:32.360 --> 03:34.600
Fengnian, pardon my intrusion.

03:34.840 --> 03:36.370
What are you talking about?

03:36.560 --> 03:38.290
I just arrived late last night.

03:38.640 --> 03:42.640
And went to the military camp early this morning for official business.

03:43.040 --> 03:44.120
Yunkui,

03:44.880 --> 03:46.680
is everything alright with him?

03:46.680 --> 03:47.640
He's fine.

03:48.320 --> 03:49.520
What could be wrong?

03:50.079 --> 03:52.160
It's just that the fighting at the front is fierce,

03:52.160 --> 03:53.960
and communication is often cut off.

03:53.960 --> 03:55.960
We are also waiting for his latest battle report.

03:55.960 --> 03:57.920
Commander Sun is back.

03:58.120 --> 03:59.079
Fengnian.

03:59.360 --> 04:01.600
Our families have been friends for years.

04:01.600 --> 04:04.120
If anything has happened to Yunkui,

04:04.520 --> 04:06.560
you must tell me the truth.

04:09.080 --> 04:10.880
Uncle, please sit down.

04:11.240 --> 04:12.480
Take a seat.

04:20.360 --> 04:23.560
My coffin has long been prepared.

04:24.480 --> 04:25.740
I've thought about it.

04:26.400 --> 04:29.360
If Yunkui dies heroically for his country this time,

04:29.640 --> 04:31.080
let him use it first.

04:31.400 --> 04:32.720
I can take it.

04:32.720 --> 04:34.600
Uncle, don't overthink.

04:35.040 --> 04:37.570
I'll report to you as soon as there is any news.

04:38.880 --> 04:40.720
He wrote a few days ago,

04:41.120 --> 04:43.080
saying he was guarding the Bai Family Residence.

04:43.080 --> 04:43.840
Yes.

04:44.000 --> 04:45.520
But, look,

04:45.800 --> 04:47.440
Dachang has been lost.

04:47.600 --> 04:48.360
Then,

04:48.360 --> 04:50.720
has his position been lost too?

05:07.160 --> 05:09.360
The 87th Brigade was very brave.

05:09.680 --> 05:11.000
The whole brigade,

05:12.240 --> 05:14.300
all died heroically for the country.

05:21.480 --> 05:22.440
But,

05:22.960 --> 05:24.960
we haven't found Yunkui's body yet.

05:26.640 --> 05:28.040
What does that mean?

05:28.600 --> 05:29.640
The higher-ups' order

05:29.640 --> 05:31.080
was to defend the position to the death.

05:31.080 --> 05:32.600
But Yunkui and over fifty brothers

05:32.600 --> 05:33.960
were not on the position,

05:33.960 --> 05:35.360
so we couldn't find them.

05:35.640 --> 05:37.370
It's hard to draw a conclusion.

05:37.600 --> 05:38.920
Conclusion?

05:43.120 --> 05:44.720
What conclusion?

05:46.720 --> 05:48.520
Do you mean

05:49.240 --> 05:51.000
he deserted in the face of battle?

05:51.000 --> 05:51.440
I,

05:51.560 --> 05:52.720
I don't mean that.

05:53.159 --> 05:54.820
But Dachang is lost after all,

05:54.880 --> 05:57.810
and the higher-ups are holding people accountable.

06:00.520 --> 06:01.640
So,

06:02.120 --> 06:04.520
there's still a glimmer of hope for Yunkui.

06:04.840 --> 06:07.320
But the position was lost.

06:07.600 --> 06:09.130
According to military law,

06:09.640 --> 06:10.320
even if he is alive,

06:10.320 --> 06:12.600
it's a dead end.

06:19.680 --> 06:20.880
Please have some tea.

06:23.720 --> 06:25.760
I believe in Yunkui.

06:28.840 --> 06:31.200
You believe in him too, right?

06:33.560 --> 06:34.640
Uncle.

07:06.600 --> 07:07.280
Please.

07:07.440 --> 07:07.840
Uncle.

07:08.080 --> 07:08.920
Please don't.

07:08.920 --> 07:09.600
I believe Yunkui.

07:09.600 --> 07:10.280
I really do.

07:19.960 --> 07:21.760
What exactly is going on?

07:23.200 --> 07:24.160
Say something.

07:24.160 --> 07:25.920
Bastards, idiots.

07:25.920 --> 07:26.980
A bunch of cowards.

07:28.200 --> 07:29.960
None of you are of any use.

07:46.480 --> 07:47.600
Are you hurt?

07:51.320 --> 07:52.520
Is it serious?

07:52.680 --> 07:54.409
Which hospital are they in now?

08:05.880 --> 08:07.760
I haven't had a hot meal in days.

08:08.520 --> 08:09.680
Thank you, ma'am.

08:19.320 --> 08:20.800
Are you all back?

08:22.920 --> 08:24.400
Just tell the madam what you have to say.

08:24.400 --> 08:25.400
Don't keep us in suspense.

08:25.400 --> 08:27.130
You're making us worried sick.

08:29.400 --> 08:32.460
Military orders are mountains, don't you understand?

08:50.760 --> 08:51.440
Is it enough?

08:51.440 --> 08:52.120
If not,

08:52.160 --> 08:54.120
I'll have Aunt Liu cook some more.

08:57.120 --> 08:58.280
It's enough, ma'am.

09:00.800 --> 09:01.280
Well,

09:01.360 --> 09:02.000
ma'am,

09:02.200 --> 09:04.330
our brigade commander's strict order

09:05.720 --> 09:07.720
is that I can only tell the master.

09:08.280 --> 09:10.400
If you don't tell me where the master is,

09:10.400 --> 09:11.440
I'll go find him.

09:13.000 --> 09:14.160
Otherwise, I'll go halfway

09:14.160 --> 09:15.520
and stop him.

09:18.640 --> 09:19.560
Forget it.

09:19.960 --> 09:21.290
I'll come back tonight.

09:29.400 --> 09:30.400
Aunt Liu.

09:31.240 --> 09:31.640
Give it to me.

09:31.640 --> 09:31.880
No.

09:32.040 --> 09:32.560
Give it to me.

09:32.560 --> 09:33.560
This belongs to our family,

09:33.560 --> 09:34.240
our young master's sword.

09:34.240 --> 09:35.600
Give it to me.

09:40.720 --> 09:41.960
Ma'am.

10:15.880 --> 10:17.320
I haven't asked,

10:18.280 --> 10:19.480
what's your name?

10:21.200 --> 10:22.560
I...

10:23.680 --> 10:25.120
My name is Meng Wanfu.

10:25.920 --> 10:28.050
I am the brigade commander's orderly.

10:28.560 --> 10:31.280
Tell me your brigade commander's orders.

10:32.440 --> 10:34.120
Word for word.

10:35.720 --> 10:37.320
Our brigade commander said,

10:39.120 --> 10:40.280
deliver this sword

10:41.240 --> 10:43.880
to 99 Yihe Road, Nanjing,

10:44.960 --> 10:47.520
give it to my father, Zhang Ruxian,

10:48.600 --> 10:50.320
and tell him

10:51.320 --> 10:53.250
I have done my duty for the country.

10:56.640 --> 10:58.400
Not a single word missing.

10:58.960 --> 11:00.490
Those were his exact words.

11:06.600 --> 11:08.000
Alright.

11:12.080 --> 11:14.540
Thank you for your hard work, Brother Wanfu.

11:14.920 --> 11:17.280
There is one thing I'd like to ask of you.

11:18.880 --> 11:20.540
The old master is getting old,

11:20.560 --> 11:22.290
and his health is not very good.

11:23.080 --> 11:24.280
About this matter...

11:27.360 --> 11:28.820
don't tell him about this.

11:29.520 --> 11:30.780
I will tell him myself.

11:31.600 --> 11:32.840
No, ma'am.

11:33.080 --> 11:34.800
I swore an oath.

11:34.800 --> 11:36.920
I must deliver this sword in person.

11:38.520 --> 11:39.200
Ma'am.

11:42.360 --> 11:43.240
Ma'am.

11:45.600 --> 11:47.680
Ma'am, Master is back.

11:48.520 --> 11:49.560
Master.

11:50.280 --> 11:51.600
Hurry up. I know.

11:51.840 --> 11:53.160
Get out of here. Come.

11:53.160 --> 11:55.220
You don't beg inside someone's home.

11:55.560 --> 11:57.400
I'll go get you some food in the front yard.

11:57.400 --> 11:58.320
Yujiao.

12:00.360 --> 12:01.800
Dad is back.

12:02.000 --> 12:03.560
I saw Liao Fengnian.

12:04.280 --> 12:05.880
Yunkui is still at the front.

12:06.360 --> 12:07.640
He's fighting well.

12:08.040 --> 12:09.440
But the latest war report

12:09.440 --> 12:10.570
hasn't come out yet.

12:10.680 --> 12:12.120
We have to wait for news.

12:12.800 --> 12:13.280
Get out.

12:14.120 --> 12:15.160
I'll see you out.

12:16.680 --> 12:17.160
Go.

12:17.800 --> 12:18.720
Get out.

12:18.840 --> 12:20.200
I'm begging you, get out.

12:20.200 --> 12:21.280
Stop.

12:27.320 --> 12:28.360
Come here.

12:48.560 --> 12:49.800
You're a soldier.

13:08.600 --> 13:10.320
Are you from the 87th Brigade?

13:28.160 --> 13:29.360
Father.

13:37.400 --> 13:38.680
You found out.

14:18.720 --> 14:22.840
The brave steed dies in battle,

14:23.880 --> 14:27.320
while the old nag wanders and whinnies.

14:36.240 --> 14:38.640
My son died a worthy death.

14:41.880 --> 14:44.680
A worthy death indeed.

15:11.680 --> 15:13.560
Young Master.

15:20.200 --> 15:21.520
Master,

15:22.880 --> 15:24.680
an entire brigade

15:25.680 --> 15:29.040
was wiped out.

15:30.520 --> 15:32.240
Young Master.

15:51.920 --> 15:53.280
Young man.

15:54.480 --> 15:56.940
When your brigade commander died in battle,

15:58.200 --> 16:00.160
you were right beside him.

16:03.960 --> 16:05.120
Yes.

16:08.960 --> 16:11.800
Tell me exactly how your brigade commander died,

16:12.320 --> 16:13.560
in full detail,

16:14.000 --> 16:16.560
without leaving out a single word.

16:30.920 --> 16:32.160
Don't be afraid.

16:32.360 --> 16:33.680
Tell Deputy Commander Liao

16:33.680 --> 16:35.720
exactly what you told me.

16:36.040 --> 16:37.360
Be truthful,

16:37.600 --> 16:39.280
and don't exaggerate.

16:41.080 --> 16:42.440
Speak.

16:46.280 --> 16:48.440
Don't worry, Uncle.

16:49.360 --> 16:50.290
Little brother,

16:50.560 --> 16:51.560
tell the truth.

16:51.800 --> 16:54.000
Just say what you saw with your own eyes.

16:58.720 --> 17:02.200
Our front line was too miserable.

17:03.360 --> 17:05.680
The enemy's artillery fire was too fierce.

17:05.680 --> 17:07.210
They bombed during the day,

17:07.480 --> 17:08.400
and at night.

17:08.720 --> 17:10.880
Then during the day again.

17:11.760 --> 17:14.400
Our trenches were full of water.

17:14.640 --> 17:16.079
We were soaking in that water

17:16.079 --> 17:17.520
all day long.

17:17.680 --> 17:19.079
Talk about Zhang Yunkui.

17:20.560 --> 17:21.480
Yes.

17:21.839 --> 17:23.680
Our brigade commander,

17:24.160 --> 17:25.520
he was simply amazing.

17:25.760 --> 17:26.920
He ordered his men

17:27.280 --> 17:28.520
to use mortars

17:28.880 --> 17:30.280
and machine guns,

17:30.440 --> 17:31.500
Machine gun nests.

17:31.560 --> 17:32.880
Yes, machine gun nests,

17:32.880 --> 17:33.940
and hand grenades,

17:34.120 --> 17:37.200
to attack the enemy's wave formation.

17:37.320 --> 17:38.120
Wave formation.

17:38.120 --> 17:39.450
Right, wave formation.

17:39.560 --> 17:40.720
Anyway, they repelled

17:40.720 --> 17:42.760
batch after batch of enemies.

17:43.040 --> 17:43.880
Our brigade commander

17:43.880 --> 17:46.120
predicted things like a god,

17:46.280 --> 17:47.480
just like Zhuge Liang.

17:47.480 --> 17:48.360
You see,

17:48.640 --> 17:50.160
Yunkui is just like this.

17:50.520 --> 17:52.400
He is a qualified soldier.

17:53.080 --> 17:54.040
Yes.

17:54.480 --> 17:55.960
Go on.

17:57.200 --> 17:59.200
Anyway, our Baijiazhai

17:59.560 --> 18:00.880
fought very hard.

18:01.280 --> 18:02.320
I remember

18:02.800 --> 18:04.640
it was the night of the Mid-Autumn Festival.

18:04.640 --> 18:05.840
There were only

18:05.960 --> 18:07.920
over 400 brothers left on our position.

18:07.920 --> 18:09.080
The brigade commander said

18:09.080 --> 18:11.600
the higher-ups asked us to hold out for another three days.

18:11.600 --> 18:13.120
But half of our brothers

18:13.600 --> 18:15.200
would die in one day.

18:15.440 --> 18:17.720
There weren't enough people to die for three days.

18:17.720 --> 18:18.560
We heard long ago

18:18.560 --> 18:20.360
that there would be reinforcements from Liuzhen

18:20.360 --> 18:21.280
to support us.

18:21.640 --> 18:23.120
But three days after three days,

18:23.120 --> 18:25.400
we didn't see a shadow of the reinforcements.

18:25.400 --> 18:26.560
The brigade commander said,

18:26.560 --> 18:28.360
Then we will go and meet the reinforcements.

18:28.360 --> 18:30.320
But we couldn't leave the position.

18:30.320 --> 18:32.720
The telephone line to the division headquarters was also cut.

18:32.720 --> 18:34.320
Everyone argued endlessly.

18:34.520 --> 18:37.080
Our brigade commander was also extremely anxious.

18:37.080 --> 18:38.440
I made water caltrop mooncakes

18:38.440 --> 18:39.960
for our brigade commander.

18:39.960 --> 18:42.690
Although our brigade commander had no appetite,

18:42.760 --> 18:44.360
he still praised me, saying,

18:44.640 --> 18:45.600
At this time,

18:45.760 --> 18:47.520
you can try every means

18:47.720 --> 18:49.440
to make mooncakes for everyone on the Mid-Autumn Festival.

18:49.440 --> 18:51.500
You are worthy of the word 'Chinese'.

18:51.680 --> 18:53.540
Pick the important points to say.

18:53.840 --> 18:55.600
Grandpa, what is not important?

18:55.600 --> 18:56.720
Skip to the later part.

18:56.720 --> 18:57.400
If there's no beginning,

18:57.400 --> 18:58.680
how can there be an end?

19:01.120 --> 19:02.480
Tell us.

19:03.280 --> 19:04.560
That night...

19:05.320 --> 19:06.600
The brigade commander was inspecting at night.

19:06.600 --> 19:09.080
I accompanied him to distribute mooncakes to everyone.

19:09.080 --> 19:10.040
But as we were walking,

19:10.040 --> 19:11.520
he suddenly stopped.

19:11.920 --> 19:13.250
He said to our brothers,

19:13.360 --> 19:14.280
"Brothers,

19:14.480 --> 19:16.840
this is the position we built.

19:17.200 --> 19:18.660
We will guard it ourselves

19:18.840 --> 19:20.280
and never retreat."

19:20.440 --> 19:21.120
Actually,

19:21.360 --> 19:24.440
these were the words of Platoon Leader Wang, who had died.

19:24.440 --> 19:25.720
I didn't understand at the time

19:25.720 --> 19:26.680
why the brigade commander would repeat

19:26.680 --> 19:28.080
Platoon Leader Wang's words.

19:28.080 --> 19:29.410
Later, little brother,

19:29.640 --> 19:31.560
it doesn't matter what Platoon Leader Wang said.

19:31.560 --> 19:32.880
What did your brigade commander say?

19:32.880 --> 19:33.600
Yeah.

19:34.880 --> 19:35.480
I...

19:35.600 --> 19:37.600
Right, our brigade commander said,

19:37.960 --> 19:38.920
"Brothers,

19:39.120 --> 19:39.920
I will absolutely not

19:39.920 --> 19:41.520
let you die in vain again."

19:41.920 --> 19:42.920
After saying that,

19:42.920 --> 19:44.680
our brigade commander led fifty people

19:44.680 --> 19:46.560
as a suicide squad and set off.

19:49.880 --> 19:51.320
So you went to Liu Town.

19:52.520 --> 19:54.360
Our brigade commander wanted to take care of me,

19:54.360 --> 19:55.490
so he told me not to go

19:55.720 --> 19:56.800
and let me go home.

19:57.360 --> 19:58.360
Could I leave?

19:58.840 --> 19:59.880
I couldn't.

20:00.240 --> 20:02.080
I wanted to be with my brothers.

20:02.480 --> 20:04.540
I volunteered for the suicide squad.

20:04.720 --> 20:05.800
I wanted to go with them

20:05.800 --> 20:07.000
to bring reinforcements back

20:07.000 --> 20:08.720
within a day and a night.

20:11.240 --> 20:12.760
Are you guys wondering

20:12.960 --> 20:14.200
why I stayed

20:14.400 --> 20:15.800
and why I didn't leave?

20:17.680 --> 20:18.540
Let me tell you.

20:18.600 --> 20:19.440
It's because

20:19.440 --> 20:21.120
I fought a bloody battle alongside

20:21.120 --> 20:23.160
the brothers of the 87th Brigade.

20:23.520 --> 20:24.320
You don't know

20:24.440 --> 20:26.600
how fierce and brutal

20:26.840 --> 20:27.800
the battle at Baijiazhai was.

20:27.800 --> 20:30.160
The machine guns went rat-a-tat,

20:30.440 --> 20:32.640
and the Mauser pistols went bang-bang.

20:32.680 --> 20:33.520
And the grenades...

20:33.520 --> 20:35.080
Boom.

20:35.320 --> 20:36.480
Especially our brigade commander,

20:36.480 --> 20:37.440
who took the mortar

20:37.440 --> 20:39.000
and aimed it at the charging Japanese soldiers,

20:39.000 --> 20:40.730
firing one, two, three rounds.

20:40.920 --> 20:45.320
Boom, crash, thump, bang!

20:46.960 --> 20:48.400
The whole position

20:50.120 --> 20:51.480
went quiet.

20:53.840 --> 20:55.760
We won.

20:58.320 --> 20:59.760
Have some water.

21:00.520 --> 21:01.400
Listen.

21:01.600 --> 21:03.600
This is the real battle situation.

21:04.480 --> 21:07.160
I know exactly what happened at the Bai family mansion.

21:07.160 --> 21:08.890
When did you arrive at Liu Town?

21:10.960 --> 21:12.000
Reporting, sir.

21:12.680 --> 21:14.280
Early the next morning,

21:14.600 --> 21:15.860
we arrived at Liu Town.

21:16.040 --> 21:17.500
But when we got to Liu Town,

21:18.000 --> 21:19.280
there was no one there.

21:19.600 --> 21:21.080
We didn't even see a hair

21:21.080 --> 21:22.340
of the 159th Division.

21:22.520 --> 21:23.800
Like a bunch of idiots,

21:24.120 --> 21:26.000
we rushed to Liu Town for nothing.

21:26.520 --> 21:27.800
We only realized when we arrived

21:27.800 --> 21:29.800
that those people had already fled.

21:30.320 --> 21:31.080
The brigade commander said,

21:31.080 --> 21:33.000
'Let's quickly retreat to Baijiazhai.'

21:33.000 --> 21:34.240
Before he could finish,

21:34.240 --> 21:35.960
the enemy's main force

21:37.760 --> 21:39.120
advanced on us.

21:40.120 --> 21:41.720
Our brigade commander said,

21:41.960 --> 21:43.680
'The fortifications here are good.

21:43.680 --> 21:44.880
We can't go back.

21:45.360 --> 21:46.960
We will fight the enemy here.

21:47.800 --> 21:49.320
And we will die here.'

21:49.920 --> 21:51.200
'Brothers,

21:52.160 --> 21:53.960
if we die, we die together.'

21:55.680 --> 21:58.360
Our brigade commander wanted to leave me behind

21:59.760 --> 22:01.240
to watch them die.

22:01.840 --> 22:03.280
But he also said,

22:04.200 --> 22:05.640
'You have to live.'

22:08.040 --> 22:09.360
'If you survive,

22:09.760 --> 22:11.220
you must, for our brigade,

22:11.440 --> 22:12.640
spread a good name.'

22:12.960 --> 22:15.920
'Tell them that Chinese soldiers, until death,

22:16.360 --> 22:18.720
always faced the front lines.

22:19.200 --> 22:20.800
None of us retreated.

22:21.000 --> 22:22.680
None of us were cowards.'

22:24.080 --> 22:25.280
That day,

22:25.680 --> 22:27.200
we fought from the morning

22:28.560 --> 22:30.480
until the afternoon.

22:33.320 --> 22:34.600
I really just watched them

22:34.600 --> 22:37.040
die, one by one.

22:38.320 --> 22:39.440
Staff Officer Xie.

22:40.480 --> 22:41.520
Adjutant Zhao.

22:43.440 --> 22:44.760
Blind Huang.

22:45.280 --> 22:46.280
Xiu'er.

22:46.800 --> 22:48.240
Iron Tower.

22:48.960 --> 22:50.490
And the Brigade Commander.

22:53.320 --> 22:55.440
They really all died

22:55.560 --> 22:57.800
right in front of my eyes, one by one.

22:58.680 --> 23:00.240
Even now,

23:00.640 --> 23:03.120
I see their faces in my dreams.

23:22.160 --> 23:23.400
Uncle.

23:28.960 --> 23:31.120
My son, Yunkui,

23:32.920 --> 23:35.120
Yunkui, my son,

23:37.240 --> 23:39.880
died for his country.

23:41.600 --> 23:44.960
His loyalty is clear as the sun and moon.

23:45.560 --> 23:47.560
You died a worthy death.

23:48.440 --> 23:52.040
My son died a worthy death.

24:04.080 --> 24:05.480
Little brother,

24:06.120 --> 24:09.160
you are my son Yunkui's

24:09.520 --> 24:11.040
good comrade.

24:12.440 --> 24:13.600
Master.

24:13.880 --> 24:15.480
I am the Brigade Commander's soldier.

24:15.480 --> 24:17.360
Even if the Brigade Commander sacrificed himself,

24:17.360 --> 24:18.620
I am still his soldier.

24:18.960 --> 24:19.680
Yes.

24:19.840 --> 24:21.570
You will always be his soldier,

24:21.760 --> 24:24.400
always his comrade.

24:25.040 --> 24:26.120
You...

24:30.520 --> 24:32.920
Uncle, this matter is of great importance.

24:33.400 --> 24:35.320
I must report it to my superiors immediately.

24:35.320 --> 24:36.440
Fengnian,

24:36.800 --> 24:37.760
given our relationship,

24:37.760 --> 24:39.560
let's not talk about this.

24:40.200 --> 24:42.480
Yunkui's posthumous reputation

24:43.640 --> 24:45.440
depends entirely on you.

24:46.160 --> 24:47.120
Uncle.

24:47.720 --> 24:49.600
Yunkui and I were like brothers.

24:50.280 --> 24:52.000
This matter is of great importance.

24:52.000 --> 24:53.240
It's my duty.

24:54.080 --> 24:55.160
Please.

24:55.480 --> 24:58.080
Uncle, please accept my condolences.

24:58.600 --> 24:59.860
Go back and rest early.

24:59.920 --> 25:01.780
I'll draft the report right away.

25:02.480 --> 25:05.080
Little brother, let's go.

25:10.720 --> 25:11.760
Wait.

25:13.520 --> 25:14.840
He stays.

25:19.920 --> 25:21.240
China will win.

25:21.520 --> 25:22.980
The survival of our nation

25:23.040 --> 25:24.400
depends on this battle.

25:24.480 --> 25:26.160
Down with the Japanese invaders.

25:26.160 --> 25:27.480
China will win.

25:27.560 --> 25:29.120
The survival of our nation

25:29.240 --> 25:30.440
depends on this battle.

25:30.440 --> 25:31.920
Down with the Japanese invaders.

25:31.920 --> 25:33.560
China will win.

25:35.280 --> 25:36.200
Officer,

25:36.680 --> 25:37.840
where are we going?

25:40.280 --> 25:41.360
The military camp.

25:42.880 --> 25:43.880
What's your name?

25:44.320 --> 25:45.520
My name is Kong Erbao.

25:45.880 --> 25:47.040
When did you join the army?

25:47.040 --> 25:47.880
The survival of our nation

25:47.880 --> 25:49.210
depends on this battle.

25:49.240 --> 25:50.680
Down with the Japanese invaders.

25:50.680 --> 25:51.760
China will win.

25:52.200 --> 25:53.640
The survival of our nation

25:53.640 --> 25:54.970
depends on this battle.

25:55.120 --> 25:56.520
Down with the Japanese invaders.

25:56.520 --> 25:57.440
China will win.

25:57.600 --> 25:59.400
How long have you been a soldier?

25:59.560 --> 26:00.890
Depends on this battle.

26:01.040 --> 26:02.900
Down with the Japanese invaders.

26:03.520 --> 26:04.560
Officer,

26:04.760 --> 26:05.960
to tell you the truth,

26:08.840 --> 26:10.560
I was conscripted

26:10.840 --> 26:12.000
on August 13th.

26:14.400 --> 26:15.240
Officer,

26:15.240 --> 26:17.520
our Brigade Commander wanted to keep me here

26:17.520 --> 26:19.160
and watch them die one by one.

26:19.560 --> 26:21.360
I thought he was just saying it out of anger.

26:21.360 --> 26:22.420
But I didn't expect

26:22.800 --> 26:24.280
to actually see them

26:24.320 --> 26:25.480
die one by one.

26:25.880 --> 26:26.640
Sir,

26:26.800 --> 26:27.880
our brigade commander said

26:27.880 --> 26:29.120
he wanted me to live.

26:29.280 --> 26:30.560
But I didn't expect him

26:31.280 --> 26:32.210
to trade his life

26:33.040 --> 26:34.960
for mine.

26:36.120 --> 26:37.280
Enough.

26:38.160 --> 26:40.560
Did you see your brigade commander's body?

26:40.880 --> 26:42.320
Did you see it with your own eyes?

26:42.320 --> 26:43.480
When he told me to go,

26:43.480 --> 26:44.640
I looked back.

26:45.240 --> 26:46.080
He...

26:46.480 --> 26:47.800
he was blown up.

27:22.160 --> 27:23.160
Get out of the car.

27:36.240 --> 27:37.570
Where are we going, sir?

27:39.320 --> 27:40.040
Take this.

27:42.840 --> 27:44.240
What does this mean, sir?

27:44.520 --> 27:45.520
Leave Nanjing.

27:46.200 --> 27:47.360
And don't ever see

27:47.360 --> 27:48.240
your brigade commander's family again.

27:48.240 --> 27:49.160
Why?

27:49.720 --> 27:51.600
Aren't I supposed to testify for him?

27:51.600 --> 27:52.320
You are a deserter.

27:52.320 --> 27:53.520
Can your words be taken as evidence?

27:53.520 --> 27:55.160
No, what do you mean, sir?

27:55.200 --> 27:56.530
You are just a deserter.

27:56.560 --> 27:57.680
I could shoot you right now.

27:57.680 --> 27:58.760
I didn't desert.

27:59.000 --> 28:00.480
Our brigade commander told me to leave.

28:00.480 --> 28:01.720
In front of our grandpa,

28:01.720 --> 28:03.400
didn't I explain it to you clearly?

28:03.400 --> 28:04.600
You can't...

28:49.680 --> 28:53.040
Only iron, only blood,

28:53.360 --> 28:56.720
only iron and blood can save China!

28:57.360 --> 29:00.440
Return our mountains and rivers, vow to destroy the enemy.

29:00.440 --> 29:03.280
Awaken our national soul, vow to wipe out this humiliation.

29:03.280 --> 29:06.840
The wind is bleak, the rain is sorrowful,

29:07.120 --> 29:09.000
floods ravage the southwest,

29:09.080 --> 29:10.740
beasts devour the northeast.

29:10.920 --> 29:13.680
Can't hold back the fire in the heart,

29:13.800 --> 29:16.520
can't resist the passion in the heart.

29:16.720 --> 29:18.560
Arise, arise!

29:18.560 --> 29:20.400
Unite, everyone, unite!

29:20.520 --> 29:23.760
Strive, strive to kill the enemy!

29:24.440 --> 29:27.960
Only iron, only blood,

29:28.320 --> 29:31.840
only iron and blood can save China!

29:32.280 --> 29:35.280
Return our mountains and rivers, vow to destroy the enemy.

29:35.280 --> 29:38.240
Awaken our national soul, vow to wipe out this humiliation.

29:38.240 --> 29:41.720
The wind is bleak, the rain is sorrowful,

29:42.120 --> 29:43.960
floods ravage the southwest,

29:43.960 --> 29:45.620
beasts devour the northeast.

29:45.880 --> 29:48.640
Can't hold back the fire in the heart,

29:48.840 --> 29:51.320
can't resist the passion in the heart.

29:51.640 --> 29:53.200
Arise, arise!

29:53.440 --> 29:55.440
Unite, everyone, unite!

29:55.440 --> 29:58.760
Strive, strive to kill the enemy!

29:59.200 --> 30:02.960
Only iron, only blood,

30:03.120 --> 30:06.880
only iron and blood can save China!

30:07.120 --> 30:10.160
Return our mountains and rivers, vow to destroy the enemy.

30:10.160 --> 30:13.200
Awaken our national soul, vow to wipe out this humiliation.

30:13.200 --> 30:16.640
The wind is bleak, the rain is sorrowful,

30:16.880 --> 30:18.760
floods ravage the southwest,

30:18.760 --> 30:20.420
beasts devour the northeast.

30:20.640 --> 30:23.560
Can't hold back the fire in the heart!

30:25.560 --> 30:27.360
Sir, I can bandage wounds.

30:28.080 --> 30:30.000
Sir, let me in.

30:30.280 --> 30:30.960
I am a doctor.

30:30.960 --> 30:33.040
My family has practiced medicine for four generations.

30:33.040 --> 30:34.880
Make way, step aside!

30:34.880 --> 30:35.940
Severely wounded!

30:37.800 --> 30:38.600
Right away!

30:38.600 --> 30:40.160
Hold on, we're almost there!

30:40.160 --> 30:41.840
Doctor!

30:46.160 --> 30:47.960
Doctor, come here quickly!

30:47.960 --> 30:49.440
Hurry, heavy bleeding!

30:51.720 --> 30:53.200
Step aside!

30:56.480 --> 30:58.120
Everyone, make way!

30:58.560 --> 31:00.240
You can't just walk into a field hospital.

31:00.240 --> 31:01.200
No entry!

31:01.480 --> 31:01.960
Gently.

31:08.840 --> 31:10.680
Slow down.

31:15.960 --> 31:17.280
Sir, I can carry water.

31:17.280 --> 31:18.400
I can carry stretchers.

31:18.400 --> 31:19.200
I can help.

31:19.600 --> 31:20.680
Just put him here.

31:21.280 --> 31:22.400
Whether he lives or dies

31:22.400 --> 31:23.640
depends on his luck.

31:23.880 --> 31:25.120
Let's go.

31:34.480 --> 31:35.240
Doctor.

31:39.920 --> 31:41.200
He's hurt so badly.

31:42.320 --> 31:44.000
It should be a concussion injury.

31:44.000 --> 31:45.560
Why was it delayed for so long?

31:45.560 --> 31:46.480
Which unit brought him?

31:46.480 --> 31:47.210
I don't know.

31:47.280 --> 31:48.320
He was thrown at the door.

31:48.320 --> 31:50.120
He didn't even have a stretcher.

31:51.560 --> 31:52.960
Stretcher, stretcher!

32:31.160 --> 32:33.000
Brother Yunkui.

32:57.560 --> 32:58.680
Dad,

32:59.040 --> 33:00.280
I'm worried.

33:01.360 --> 33:03.440
Wanfu still isn't back this late.

33:03.640 --> 33:04.600
Why on earth did

33:04.600 --> 33:06.200
Liao Fengnian keep him here?

33:06.280 --> 33:07.360
Well,

33:08.000 --> 33:10.120
since Liao Fengnian agreed,

33:10.360 --> 33:12.400
he will definitely do his best.

33:13.040 --> 33:14.800
We should trust him.

33:45.920 --> 33:47.380
Wontons, soup dumplings,

33:48.000 --> 33:48.960
and spiced eggs!

33:53.000 --> 33:53.960
Hurry.

33:57.040 --> 33:57.800
You're in the way.

33:57.800 --> 33:58.400
Excuse me.

34:07.400 --> 34:09.199
Tickets to Wuhan are available!

34:09.199 --> 34:10.440
Tickets are available!

34:10.440 --> 34:11.480
To Wuhan!

34:13.440 --> 34:14.440
Who stepped on me?

34:14.960 --> 34:15.760
Don't push!

34:16.520 --> 34:18.520
Three tickets to Wuhan, just three!

34:19.000 --> 34:21.080
I just need one, one to Wuhan!

34:21.080 --> 34:21.960
Stop pushing!

34:22.080 --> 34:23.000
Stop yelling!

34:23.239 --> 34:24.280
We're in line!

34:25.040 --> 34:25.840
Stop pushing!

34:25.880 --> 34:26.880
Who stepped on you?

34:26.880 --> 34:27.400
Line up!

34:27.400 --> 34:28.719
Buy one for me, thanks!

34:28.840 --> 34:30.440
Who's gonna buy one for you? We all need tickets!

34:30.440 --> 34:32.239
Stop yelling! We're all in line!

34:33.600 --> 34:35.400
One for me!

34:36.840 --> 34:37.600
Don't push!

34:37.600 --> 34:39.120
One to Wuhan!

34:40.239 --> 34:41.560
Two to Wuhan!

34:46.600 --> 34:47.400
Who cut in line?

34:47.400 --> 34:48.360
I was just here!

34:48.639 --> 34:49.400
Move!

34:49.880 --> 34:50.679
To Wuhan.

34:51.920 --> 34:52.960
How much to Wuhan?

34:53.520 --> 34:54.050
Sold out.

34:55.159 --> 34:56.239
You think you're right to cut in line?

34:56.239 --> 34:58.080
No, it's only been selling for a few minutes.

34:58.080 --> 34:59.360
Move!

35:00.200 --> 35:01.160
What about tomorrow's?

35:01.160 --> 35:01.800
Tomorrow's?

35:01.800 --> 35:02.440
None.

35:02.600 --> 35:04.880
Hankou direction sold out. Payment received.

35:04.880 --> 35:05.880
The day after tomorrow.

35:05.880 --> 35:07.320
Any day is fine.

35:07.560 --> 35:09.160
Come line up early tomorrow.

35:15.400 --> 35:16.360
Stop pushing!

35:16.960 --> 35:17.800
Sold out!

35:17.800 --> 35:18.440
That's what you get for cutting!

35:18.440 --> 35:19.440
Any luck getting in front?

35:19.440 --> 35:20.000
None of your business.

35:20.000 --> 35:20.400
Did you get one?

35:20.400 --> 35:21.080
Sold out.

35:38.240 --> 35:40.000
87th Brigade, Meng Wanfu.

35:40.440 --> 35:42.900
Do you know Meng Wanfu from the 87th Brigade?

35:43.480 --> 35:45.600
87th Brigade, Meng Wanfu.

35:47.040 --> 35:49.500
Do you know Meng Wanfu from the 87th Brigade?

35:51.400 --> 35:53.360
87th Brigade, Meng Wanfu.

36:24.920 --> 36:29.240
87th Brigade, Meng Wanfu.

36:32.120 --> 36:34.480
What will this child do?

36:36.240 --> 36:37.800
Yujiao,

36:37.960 --> 36:39.800
what will you do?

36:40.000 --> 36:41.930
Sister-in-law, please don't cry.

36:42.760 --> 36:43.920
If you keep crying,

36:44.320 --> 36:46.250
I won't be able to hold it in either.

36:48.120 --> 36:49.160
Liao Fengnian,

36:49.440 --> 36:50.320
come out!

36:50.520 --> 36:52.320
Yujiao has been here for a while.

36:57.760 --> 36:58.720
You're here.

36:59.840 --> 37:00.680
Brother Liao.

37:00.840 --> 37:02.040
That soldier from yesterday,

37:02.040 --> 37:04.120
did you take him to see your commander?

37:04.120 --> 37:05.280
Yes.

37:06.240 --> 37:07.560
What did they say?

37:08.440 --> 37:09.680
No clear answer.

37:10.400 --> 37:11.560
What do you mean?

37:12.600 --> 37:14.280
It's quite complicated.

37:14.360 --> 37:15.680
Come, take a seat.

37:20.440 --> 37:22.970
The superiors haven't made a clear decision.

37:23.480 --> 37:25.880
I can't really say much.

37:26.400 --> 37:28.260
But you need to prepare yourself.

37:28.600 --> 37:30.040
Prepare for what?

37:31.160 --> 37:33.040
It's just our...

37:33.600 --> 37:35.080
this damn rule.

37:35.520 --> 37:37.320
If a man dies on the battlefield,

37:37.840 --> 37:39.000
he died for the country.

37:39.000 --> 37:41.000
If he doesn't die on the battlefield,

37:41.000 --> 37:42.520
it's desertion.

37:44.680 --> 37:46.480
Desertion?

37:54.560 --> 37:55.640
You...

37:57.200 --> 37:59.320
Your theater commander,

38:00.160 --> 38:02.760
army commander, division commander, and corps commander,

38:02.760 --> 38:04.560
that's how they labeled Yunkui.

38:07.760 --> 38:10.240
You want to make him your scapegoat.

38:17.560 --> 38:18.820
Where is that soldier?

38:19.080 --> 38:20.600
Give that soldier to me.

38:20.720 --> 38:22.080
I'll take him to see your commanding officer.

38:22.080 --> 38:23.160
I'll go talk to them.

38:23.160 --> 38:25.160
It's useless no matter who you go to.

38:25.360 --> 38:27.040
I've tried finding people and arguing with them.

38:27.040 --> 38:29.040
I even fell out with our corps and division commanders.

38:29.040 --> 38:29.840
As for Yunkui's matter,

38:29.840 --> 38:31.040
it didn't help at all.

38:32.640 --> 38:34.480
The Battle of Shanghai turned out like this,

38:34.480 --> 38:35.200
from the Generalissimo

38:35.200 --> 38:36.440
down to the theater commanders.

38:36.440 --> 38:37.080
The division commander, the corps commander,

38:37.080 --> 38:38.400
who isn't responsible?

38:38.400 --> 38:39.660
Bringing up Yunkui now

38:40.280 --> 38:41.720
won't help.

38:43.200 --> 38:45.120
Nanjing is in grave danger now.

38:45.520 --> 38:47.520
It's not like what the newspapers say.

38:47.520 --> 38:48.000
You know

38:48.000 --> 38:49.120
about the old man's health

38:49.120 --> 38:49.980
and his temper.

38:50.520 --> 38:51.720
Take my advice.

38:52.600 --> 38:54.040
Leave Nanjing

38:54.560 --> 38:55.920
as soon as you can.

38:59.040 --> 38:59.970
Sister-in-law.

39:00.080 --> 39:01.680
I, Liao Fengnian, right to your face,

39:01.680 --> 39:02.720
swear to you,

39:03.160 --> 39:06.760
that I will definitely overturn Yunkui's case in this lifetime.

39:08.800 --> 39:09.960
Overturn the case?

39:11.680 --> 39:13.810
This matter has already been settled.

39:17.560 --> 39:18.960
Where is that soldier?

39:19.480 --> 39:21.080
He promised to return to our house yesterday.

39:21.080 --> 39:23.340
We waited all night but he didn't show up.

39:23.920 --> 39:25.640
Where did you take him?

39:28.560 --> 39:29.640
Liao,

39:30.120 --> 39:31.400
look me in the eye.

39:34.920 --> 39:36.580
When Yunkui and I got married,

39:37.200 --> 39:39.040
you were our witness.

39:39.960 --> 39:40.920
We also agreed that

39:40.920 --> 39:42.560
after our child was born,

39:42.760 --> 39:44.560
they would call you and your wife

39:44.720 --> 39:46.520
their godfather and godmother.

39:47.800 --> 39:49.600
That soldier crawled out

39:49.600 --> 39:50.860
from a pile of corpses.

39:51.960 --> 39:53.080
He walked to Nanjing

39:53.080 --> 39:54.480
like a ghost, step by step,

39:54.480 --> 39:55.760
just to hand Yunkui's sword

39:55.760 --> 39:57.560
to me personally.

39:58.800 --> 40:00.320
He was Yunkui's soldier,

40:00.720 --> 40:02.880
so he is my brother.

40:03.760 --> 40:06.020
Liao, you are also Yunkui's best friend.

40:06.040 --> 40:07.280
You were comrades in arms,

40:07.280 --> 40:08.720
brothers who would die for each other.

40:08.720 --> 40:09.880
Publicly or privately,

40:09.880 --> 40:11.960
you should tell me where

40:12.560 --> 40:13.720
that soldier is.

40:13.720 --> 40:15.960
Liao Fengnian, say something!

40:17.240 --> 40:18.440
Sister-in-law,

40:19.720 --> 40:20.960
let me put it this way.

40:21.240 --> 40:22.320
Someone wants this soldier

40:22.320 --> 40:24.650
to completely disappear from this world.

40:27.120 --> 40:29.480
You want to silence him.

40:31.120 --> 40:32.920
Just to save your face,

40:33.480 --> 40:34.240
to shirk responsibility

40:34.240 --> 40:36.300
for your failure on the battlefield.

40:36.400 --> 40:37.520
You want to shift the blame

40:37.520 --> 40:40.250
onto a group of people who died on the battlefield

40:40.320 --> 40:42.120
and can't speak for themselves.

40:42.120 --> 40:44.200
How dare you!

40:47.360 --> 40:49.720
What kind of people are you?

40:50.120 --> 40:51.600
What kind of army is this?

40:51.760 --> 40:54.080
What kind of country is this?

40:54.920 --> 40:57.800
Yunkui's body is still in Dachang.

40:58.200 --> 40:59.120
Come here.

40:59.520 --> 41:01.120
His body is still in Dachang.

41:01.200 --> 41:02.280
His bones aren't even cold yet.

41:02.280 --> 41:05.400
Do you dare to shout towards Dachang,

41:05.520 --> 41:07.120
Zhang Yunkui?

41:07.440 --> 41:11.160
Do you dare to shout towards Dachang,

41:11.480 --> 41:13.440
87th Brigade?

41:17.960 --> 41:19.080
I let them go.

41:19.520 --> 41:21.320
They left through Yijiang Gate.

41:21.640 --> 41:23.640
They should be out of Nanjing by now.

41:29.600 --> 41:31.520
What have you done?

41:41.640 --> 41:42.280
Hello, sir.

41:42.280 --> 41:42.920
Donation for the resistance.

41:42.920 --> 41:44.380
Could you donate a little?

41:44.440 --> 41:46.160
Sir.

41:46.280 --> 41:47.640
Resist the Japanese invaders, sir.

41:47.640 --> 41:48.760
Everyone is responsible for resisting the invaders.

41:48.760 --> 41:49.600
Sir.

41:49.960 --> 41:53.440
Spiced eggs!

42:01.440 --> 42:02.240
To Wuhan.

42:04.520 --> 42:05.720
It's useless to come early.

42:05.720 --> 42:07.240
There are no tickets at the counter.

42:07.240 --> 42:09.000
The scalpers bought them all.

42:11.640 --> 42:12.840
Brother.

42:13.240 --> 42:14.440
What's a scalper?

42:14.600 --> 42:16.200
People who sell tickets at high prices.

42:16.200 --> 42:17.860
How much is a ticket from them?

42:20.720 --> 42:22.280
How much is this?

42:22.360 --> 42:23.720
One small gold bar.

42:23.800 --> 42:24.800
What?

42:25.440 --> 42:26.970
One gold bar for one ticket.

42:27.040 --> 42:28.400
Are they crazy?

42:29.840 --> 42:31.080
Not to mention cabin tickets,

42:31.080 --> 42:31.960
even cargo hold tickets

42:31.960 --> 42:33.040
have skyrocketed.

42:33.400 --> 42:34.360
Look.

42:34.720 --> 42:35.760
Everyone is bringing their families

42:35.760 --> 42:37.000
to flee to Wuhan.

42:37.040 --> 42:38.440
Learn about the resistance donation.

42:38.440 --> 42:39.880
Everyone, please donate to the resistance.

42:39.880 --> 42:40.760
Excuse me.

42:41.040 --> 42:44.320
Would you like to participate in our donation?

42:44.760 --> 42:45.890
Thank you very much.

42:46.000 --> 42:46.920
May God bless you.

42:46.920 --> 42:47.780
Have a good day.

42:52.000 --> 42:53.130
A couple of days ago,

42:53.480 --> 42:55.410
the boats didn't even dare to dock.

42:55.640 --> 42:56.400
And now,

42:56.400 --> 42:58.440
even taking a rowboat to the middle of the river

42:58.440 --> 42:59.600
costs 30 dollars.

